    1/16 in (1.25mm).
[4] Number of Coats: 2
    Sequence of Coats: 1 coat Concentrate, 1 coat Modified
    Recoat Cure Time and Temperature: 2 hours at 23ºC
    Final Cure Time and Temperature: 3 days moist cure followed by 12 days set time prior to
    water contact
    Special Comments: Mix ratio of powder:water is 5:2 by volume. Maximum film thickness is
    1/16 in (1.25mm).
[5] Number of Coats: 1
    Maximum Field Use Dry Film Thickness (in mils): 500 - 2000
    Final Cure Time and Temperature: 3 days moist cure at 72°F
    Special Comments: Mix ratio of water:powder is 0.9 gallons:55 lbs or 1 gallon:60 lbs.
